OL,3,CClosure of day care centre in Oldham
OL,4,Con hold after backlash
OL,6,FThe closure of a much-loved day care
OL,7,Fcentre for adults with learning
OL,8,Fdisabilities is on hold after a public
OL,9,Foutcry.
OL,11,FCouncil-owned care providers MioCare
OL,12,Fproposed slashing the service at
OL,13,FChadderton Hall Park, Oldham as part
OL,14,Fof budget-cutting measures, with
OL,15,FOldham Town Hall attempting to plug a
OL,16,F#20m budget gap.
