OL,3,CClosure of day care centre in Oldham
OL,4,Con hold after backlash
OL,6,FCare worker Amanda Shelley, 60, whose
OL,7,F50-year-old brother Mark Hilton
OL,8,Fattends the day-care centre every
OL,9,Fweekday between 9am and 3pm, welcomed
OL,10,Fthe news.
OL,12,FShelley said: "It's amazing news that
OL,13,Fthey're not closing it down. At least
OL,14,Fwe have got that result.
OL,16,F"We'll keep challenging it until they
OL,17,Fagree to keep it open. These are
OL,18,Fadults with special needs and they
OL,19,Fdeserve better."
