OL,6,FMark has learning difficulties and is
OL,7,Fnon-verbal. Attending 'Chaddy Hall'
OL,8,Ffor the last 20 years has "meant
OL,9,Feverything" to both him and his family.
OL,11,FPreviously, his dad John Hilton has
OL,12,Fsaid: "The staff are so caring
OL,13,Finteracting with Mark, he feels that."
OL,15,FThe day care centre provides "an
OL,16,Falternative to traditional daycare"
OL,17,Faccording to the Oldham Council
OL,18,Fwebsite.
