OL,6,FAmanda, who also acts as Mark's
OL,7,Fpersonal assistant for 15 hours a
OL,8,Fweek, says he loves playing music,
OL,9,Fwoodworking, and gardening at the
OL,10,Fcentre.
OL,12,F"All our plants are from there because
OL,13,Fthey grow them themselves," she said.
OL,15,FMark likes familiarity and routine,
OL,16,Fand his family say the day care centre
OL,17,Fhas been his world for two decades.
