OL,6,FShelley and her husband want to
OL,7,Fcampaign to raise funds for repairs to
OL,8,Fthe buildings, which MioCare has
OL,9,Fwarned could be "very costly".
OL,11,FThe care provider wanted to strike the
OL,12,Fday care centre from their books to
OL,13,Fsave the #150,000 yearly running cost
OL,14,Fand future expense of building
OL,15,Fmaintenance.
