OL,3,CClosure of day care centre in Oldham
OL,4,Con hold after backlash
OL,6,FLabour Councillor Barbara Brownridge
OL,7,Fsaid: "After listening carefully to
OL,8,Fthe responses so far to the
OL,9,Fconsultation, and to the very real and
OL,10,Funderstandable concerns raised by
OL,11,Ffamilies and carers and stakeholders
OL,12,Flike Jim McMahon MP, we have decided
OL,13,Fto pause the proposed closure of
OL,14,FChadderton Park Day Care Centre.
OL,16,F"We will now work closely with MioCare
OL,17,Fto find savings in other ways, and to
OL,18,Flook again at how we can best support
OL,19,Fthe people who rely on the Chadderton
OL,20,FPark day service.
