OL,6,F"I had understood that this
OL,7,Fconsultation had started much earlier.
OL,8,FI am disappointed to learn that it had
OL,9,Fnot, and I am sorry for the worry and
OL,10,Fdistress this has caused. We will
OL,11,Fraise this directly with MioCare."
OL,13,FAsked if they could reassure families
OL,14,Fof how long the future of the care
OL,15,Fcentre is secured for, a council
OL,16,Fspokesperson said there was currently
OL,17,F'no timescale'.
