OL,6,FThe spokesperson said: "Local
OL,7,Fcouncillors have asked for the
OL,8,Fproposals to be paused whilst further
OL,9,Finformation is gathered to understand
OL,10,Ffully the nature and impact of those
OL,11,Fproposals. That work is being
OL,12,Fundertaken now but as yet we have no
OL,13,Ftimescale for completion."
